HEADWORD: Gobline
<hw>Gob"line`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Naut.)</fld>
<def>One of the ropes or chains serving as stays for the dolphin striker
or the bowsprit; -- called also <altname>gobrope</altname> and
<altname>gaubline</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Goblinize</ent>⟦br⟧
